{"tid":1611524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"三個online game副本建議","createTime":"2019-10-02T03:36:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T10:44:01.000Z","uid":2615,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1a091b52b15625666c616b7ddd9e1aec49b88fe8","tid":1611524,"uid":2615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:36:51.000Z","msg":"第一,最前排嗰6 7 行一定唔可以背住嚟跑（自己睇情況啦當然）<br />\n背住敵人跑係會激發有捕獵嘅心態<br />\n你諗下平時班狗比人打到背住跑嘅時候,你追住佢地嘅感覺係唔同，甚至連中後排嘅人都敢衝上嚟追狗打<br />\n因為呢種係天性，追一個背對你嘅敵人係激發到人嘅捕獵心同狂性<br />\n<br />\n第二,一定要數同報比人知有幾多隻狗，中前同中後排係唔知有幾多隻狗，所以一叫有狗佢地就驚<br />\n如果報係少狗嘅，就算班狗衝都會定d<br />\n<br />\n第三,一係打，一係遊擊<br />\n呢到關乎到第二點，你數狗數得少，又搵齊腳嘅，就打啦<br />\n如果唔係就遊擊啦<br />\n班狗係戰略性嘅隊伍<br />\n只有不斷移動佢地先有機會出錯，如果唔係就等比人捉啦<br />\n佢地每行一步都要聽order<br />\n不斷咁移動，移動到佢地跟唔上order就有機會出錯<br />\n<br />\n有錯可以提出，希望可以令到隻game更易玩同打副本死少d人"},{"pid":"5c88ec587b199ab48465ccfa7b126f26ee6312de","tid":1611524,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:37:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">政府即將告你暴動！</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">只有全民<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無&middot;限&middot;期</span>罷工罷課先可以救自己、救義士！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1610341\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1610341</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">今日政府宣布，香港各區發生暴動！</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">亦即係話，今日只要出過街嘅非警察人士，都有機會告你參與暴動</span>！<span style=\"color: red;\">要去狗屋坐48個鐘，而且定罪嘅話一坐就幾年</span>！<br />\n<br />\n打工反學嘅你，為你自己將來，呼籲大家，<span style=\"color: red;\">盡快組織無限期罷工、罷課</span>！<span style=\"color: gold;\">只有咁，先可以癱瘓社會運作，直到政府宣布徹底妥協，答應五大訴求為止！</span>"},{"pid":"a4f5bd8c2e158f217e700e5d8f182eb29752e0cf","tid":1611524,"uid":2615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:37:53.000Z","msg":"自推一下<br />\n希望有多d人睇"},{"pid":"e726edd510fef0ffa406ee1ca7d6d1661ef4ff97","tid":1611524,"uid":2615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:41:18.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"d12e0f3f6de018db50a3a307c62bc118f4ecbaed","tid":1611524,"uid":2615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:50:56.000Z","msg":"屌，開錯想開喺遊戲台"},{"pid":"3d63243d6a3f03ab1b75a0d813bdd8d747bd90c3","tid":1611524,"uid":2615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:39:48.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"d70380a737978d53d420ff33b15ae642d6c231cd","tid":1611524,"uid":200623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:42:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1263f77c9e7f58d5a626918c33bad8852e168407","tid":1611524,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:43:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6dd1e975dd33230a53bcdc906b59ec7be294d8bc","tid":1611524,"uid":2615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:44:39.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"9eab4e361a8240e10483fd93ae80b4a0c7e19499","tid":1611524,"uid":186142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:48:04.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 阻阻你<br />\n唔好再指責所謂偽勇武 入嚟睇下小勇武點可以有大作為<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【實際行動戰術整合】正式宣佈下回合開始將會冇人被捕<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1611678\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1611678</a>"},{"pid":"1fd0bb13975591d503e845655338ce6fcbf029ac","tid":1611524,"uid":2615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:16:08.000Z","msg":"推一下"},{"pid":"6bb28954529da1060e1b049566de6be0283a0127","tid":1611524,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:23:45.000Z","msg":"勇氣重要"},{"pid":"04d2c49414eb9c02bb7aef5a496fa6517579517d","tid":1611524,"uid":197683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:44:01.000Z","msg":"推"}]}